# 2026-05-28: 8h-autonomous discovery outputs (203MB JSONs + PNGs, regenerable from scripts/wealth_bot/*.py)
# MD reports + INDEX.html stay tracked; bulky outputs (JSON/CSV/PNG) ignored.
runs/discovery/**/*.json
runs/discovery/**/*.csv
runs/discovery/**/*.png
runs/discovery/visual_reports*/**/*.png

runs/autonomy/

# --- experiment/session scratch (2026-06-07 git-tree cleanup): preserved on disk, kept OUT of git ---
experiments/adaptive_ma/_*
experiments/adaptive_ma/**/_*
runs/research/_*
runs/research/**/_*
scripts/autonomy/metaop/_*
# ...but DO version-control the metaop verification suite (the loop's trust harness must be reproducible on clone).
# 2026-06-07 audit G-H: previously `metaop/_*` silently ignored _test_/_proof_/_falsifier_ probes too.
!scripts/autonomy/metaop/_test_*.py
!scripts/autonomy/metaop/_proof_*.py
!scripts/autonomy/metaop/_falsifier_*.py
runs/staging/directive_proposals/_last_write.txt
**/*OUT.txt
**/*.bak

